oads/2021/02/league4.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league4-980x656.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league4.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742269\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742269\"><span></span><p>Ben Affleck is Batman.</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league5-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league5.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league5-980x640.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league5.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742270\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742270\"><span></span><p>Ray Fisher is Cyborg.</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league6-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league6.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league6-980x653.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league6.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742271\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742271\"><span></span><p>Jason Momoa is Aquaman.</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league7-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league7.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league7-980x653.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league7.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742272\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742272\"><span></span><p>Ezra Miller is The Flash.</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league15-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league15.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league15-980x651.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league15.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742280\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742280\"><span></span><p>\"You were sent here for a reason. And even if it takes the rest of your life, find out what that reason is.\"</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league14-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league14.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league14-980x645.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league14.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742279\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742279\"><span></span><p>Superman returns.</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league18-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league18.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league18-980x651.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league18.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742283\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742283\"><span></span><p>No, Cyborg, no! Don't mess with the box!</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li><li data-thumb=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league12-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league12.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/league12-980x647.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/upload