2/leagueTOP-150x150.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/leagueTOP.jpg\" data-responsive=\"https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/leagueTOP-980x653.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/leagueTOP.jpg 2560\" data-sub-html=\"#caption-1742264\"><figure><figcaption id=\"caption-1742264\"><span></span><p>A new age of heroes dawns.</p><p><span></span> YouTube/HBO Max</p></figcaption></figure></li></ul></div><p><em>Listing image by YouTube/HBO Max</em></p></div></div></div>","author":"Jennifer Ouellette","siteTitle":"Ars Technica","siteHash":"5b0ddf6e8923e49262a7894cfd77962733e43fbcc565a103b48373820b310636","entryHash":"f6548cf085229e5945db30ca0c8db2320215accb60a81f0f6d00d801c86dc50a","category":"Tech"}